{
  "texts": [
    "LLMs will require multiple teams' input during design, evaluation, and oversight.",
    "Biases are complex and require multiple teams to evaluate a model for different pockets of response types.",
    "In addition, external input will be required to ensure that a \"competitive landscape\" does not lead to conflict with data privacy or the perpetuation of biases.",
    "World-changing technology should include values from around the world.",
    "The outputs of this model that are deemed appropriate will reflect the training processes and feedback given."
  ]
}